title: #76: How Far Up The Egg Do The Pants Go?
itunes:title: #76: How Far Up The Egg Do The Pants Go?
description:
Another year in the books, can you believe it? Well, The Clue Crew is going to celebrate the only way we know how: with Riddles! And not just any riddles, some special riddle submissions from incredibly smart and good-looking listeners just like you! So join us as we cap 2019 and welcome 2020. Here's to 400 more years of this cursed podcast!

Starring:

Adal Rifai

John Patrick Coan

Erin Keif

Editing by: 

Casey Toney

Theme by: 

Arne Parrott

Logo by: 

Emily Kardamis & Emmaline Morris
